Maintainer: Adam Ladachowski <adam.ladachowski@gmail.com>
Description: Caddy web server with Cloudflare DNS plugin
 Caddy is a powerful, enterprise-ready, open source web server with
 automatic HTTPS. This build includes the Cloudflare DNS plugin for
 DNS-01 ACME challenges, allowing TLS certificate provisioning behind
 Cloudflare proxy.
